name: Tecno
excerpt: Tecno Spark 7 mobile was launched on 9th April 2021. The phone comes with a 6.52-inch touchscreen display offering a resolution of 720x1600 pixels and an aspect ratio of 20:9.
description: Tecno Spark 7 is powered by a 1.8GHz octa-core MediaTek Helio A25 processor. It comes with 2GB, 3GB of RAM. The Tecno Spark 7 runs Android 11 and is powered by a 6000mAh battery.As far as the cameras are concerned, the Tecno Spark 7 on the rear packs a 16-megapixel camera with an f/1.8 aperture. The rear camera setup has autofocus. It has a single front camera setup for selfies, featuring an 8-megapixel sensor with an f/2.0 aperture.
